videos.headline: Spencer Sanders hits Tay Martin for 30-yard Oklahoma State TD
videos.description: The Cowboys take the lead over the Sooners following Spencer Sanders' pinpoint pass to Tay Martin.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Spencer Sanders hits Tay Martin for 30-yard Oklahoma State TD) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brian Darby responds for Oklahoma with an 11-yard TD
videos.description: The Sooners get back on level terms against Oklahoma State from close range.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brian Darby responds for Oklahoma with an 11-yard TD) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tay Martin waltzes in for the easy Oklahoma State TD
videos.description: The Cowboys retake the lead against their rivals thanks to a second touchdown from Tay Martin.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tay Martin waltzes in for the easy Oklahoma State TD) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bye Bye!  Presley goes 100-yards on kickoff for TD
videos.description: Oklahoma State's Brennan Presley take the kickoff return 100 yards for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bye Bye! Presley goes 100-yards on kickoff for TD) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Austin Stogner makes sweet over-the-shoulder TD catch for Oklahoma
videos.description: Austin Stogner scores for the Sooners with an impressive TD grab.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Austin Stogner makes sweet over-the-shoulder TD catch for Oklahoma) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brayden Willis makes a leaping TD grab for Oklahoma
videos.description: The Sooners make Spencer Sanders pay for his interception with a game-tying touchdown just before halftime.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brayden Willis makes a leaping TD grab for Oklahoma ) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oklahoma takes first lead after Oklahoma State safety
videos.description: Perrion Winfrey forces the fumble, which is recovered by Oklahoma State in its own end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Oklahoma takes first lead after Oklahoma State safety) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Presley drops punt return and Oklahoma recovers for TD
videos.description: Brennan Presley has a costly mistake after dropping a punt return which Oklahoma's Justin Broiles recovers for a TD.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Presley drops punt return and Oklahoma recovers for TD) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Spencer Sanders takes it himself for 37-yard Oklahoma State TD
videos.description: Oklahoma State QB Spencer Sanders gets his team back within a field goal after a weaving run into the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Spencer Sanders takes it himself for 37-yard Oklahoma State TD) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: OU muffs punt leading to Oklahoma State's go-ahead TD
videos.description: Oklahoma's Eric Gray drops the ball and Oklahoma State retakes the lead on the ensuing drive.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (OU muffs punt leading to Oklahoma State's go-ahead TD) 2021/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oklahoma State beats Oklahoma to reach Big 12 Championship
videos.description: The Cowboys snap a six-game losing streak to the Sooners and keep their playoff hopes alive.
